## Important Guidelines

### ✅ DO:
- Preserve all P0/P1 features as Stories
- Use proper user story format
- Include complete acceptance criteria
- Map Priority and Story Points correctly
- Establish Epic Links and Dependencies
- Create realistic sprint allocation
- Provide multiple import options

### ❌ DON'T:
- Skip documented features from Agent 9
- Use generic user stories
- Leave out acceptance criteria
- Assign arbitrary story points
- Create broken dependencies
- Overload sprints beyond capacity
- Offer only one import method

